data.description:
STILL TIME TO HOST FOOTBALL! 4 BEDS PLUS STUDY! SCHEDULE YOUR SHOWING TODAY! This spacious property is perfect for families, frequent travelers (super close to the airport!), and those seeking a comfortable multigenerational living situation. If you want space, this is the place.

Step inside and marvel at the original hardwood flooring, complemented by new laminate flooring in all bedrooms. The expansive, well-appointed kitchen boasts 3 cm granite countertops, a convection oven, and cleverly designed spice cabinets, making meal prep a breeze. Entertain with ease! The spacious dining area opens to the den, which has a pass-through bar to the kitchen. You will build lifetime memories hosting football games and Thanksgiving celebrations in this warm and inviting home. Modern tech touches include a media closet, Cat-5 wiring throughout, and WiFi connected digital thermometers.

The versatile floor plan includes a dedicated office and library that can easily be a 5th bedroom. Multiple residents will each enjoy their own personal domain, with a private second suite, Jack-and-Jill bedrooms with their own bath, and a luxurious primary suite complete with a working jet tub.

Outside, indulge in the beauty of nature with a lush wildflower garden that attracts hummingbirds. You get the tranquility of country living without the cost or maintenance. The hot tub stays, providing the perfect setting for relaxation and outdoor enjoyment. 

While this section of Westbrooke Estates is not required to pay HOA dues, the HOA includes you in all of the activities throughout the year. It's the best of both worlds! 

Don't miss your chance to call this your new home. Schedule a showing today and experience all that this beautiful property has to offer! Seller reserves the right to accept an offer at any time. Contact listing agent or your agent for additional pictures.
